metadata.name: Reflexions : Looking at you looking at me
metadata.description: Reflexions is about the thought process of inner exploration, finding thy self ! The other you inside of you, the little voice with all the answers and all the solutions. It's about discovering the most incredible wonder in the universe... YOU ! If only you could take the leap, you would see that the whole universe is right there inside of you! Let the Shaman show you the way and they will show you the secrets of the universe and everything you've been missing. It all starts by your own Reflexions.
